  <lyrics>
    <stanza type="verse" number="1">Merciful and loving,
  Suff'ring pain and loss,
All for us, the sinners,
  Going to the cross;
Tasting death for all men,
  Dying for our sins;
This is Christ the Savior,
  What will you do with Him?</stanza>
